ion of expenses to overstate\nearnings.\n\nUnderstatement of allowance for loan losses or\nfor losses on investments in securities backed by\nloans.\n\nPossible overstatement of earnings via any method\nof overstatement of revenues or understatement\nof expenses.\n''"
